    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Conscience</strong> is a noir detective mystery where you play as a private investigator hired to uncover the truth behind Jack Beckham's death. Initially ruled as a suicide, Jack’s father believes otherwise and hires you to search Jack’s apartment for clues to reveal what really happened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/afc6110b18fadcae746c16c40be73bd7.poster.avif?t=1744608674\" width=600 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/afc6110b18fadcae746c16c40be73bd7.webm?t=1744608674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/afc6110b18fadcae746c16c40be73bd7.mp4?t=1744608674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Investigate and explore</u> Jack’s apartment, searching every room, shelf, and drawer for evidence and clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/51ecff4990281ea64600413dfaa90ac6.poster.avif?t=1744608674\" width=600 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/51ecff4990281ea64600413dfaa90ac6.webm?t=1744608674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/51ecff4990281ea64600413dfaa90ac6.mp4?t=1744608674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Inspect the evidence</u>, uncovering hidden details and piecing together crucial clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/be4c4930fdceda91d719f6186f55b3ea.poster.avif?t=1744608674\" width=600 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/be4c4930fdceda91d719f6186f55b3ea.webm?t=1744608674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/be4c4930fdceda91d719f6186f55b3ea.mp4?t=1744608674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Deduce</u> what truly happened using the clues you’ve gathered to solve the mystery.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/399155c790bd7cc78f8ae9418ad282d9.poster.avif?t=1744608674\" width=600 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/399155c790bd7cc78f8ae9418ad282d9.webm?t=1744608674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302650/extras/399155c790bd7cc78f8ae9418ad282d9.mp4?t=1744608674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Solve the Mystery...</u></p>",
